Fix this XState v4 fragment to v5 — invoke.src takes ctx to pick a URL:

```js
invoke: {
  src: (ctx) => fetch(`/users/${ctx.userId}`).then(r => r.json()),
  onDone: { target: 'ok', actions: assign({ user: (_, e) => e.data }) }
